The paper deals with the design of network codes for distributed storage systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT), distributed systems (cs.DS), data centers (cs.DC), network infrastructure (cs.NI), and control systems (cs.SY). The focus on regenerating codes and their performance in cloud storage systems further supports these categories.
